│   │
│ 7 │   output x content Mod_def.E
│   │                    ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾
│
│ The type definition is private because it is inside a ```catala block and
│ not a ```catala-metadata block:
├─➤ tests/modules/bad/mod_def.catala_en:12.25-26:
│    │
│ 12 │ declaration enumeration E:
│    │                         ‾
└─
#return code 123#
